{"tid":2110563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保安謂：「如果佢想起身唔使郁。」辯方質疑：「跌喺地唔郁點起身？」保安稱：「答你唔到。」","createTime":"2020-07-16T04:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T05:24:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"676143ba97edbc349a0ca6b0671f6b89be9c69e7","tid":2110563,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/CORQTPOZCBKY5QHHYVOQ67GUJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FCORQTPOZCBKY5QHHYVOQ67GUJ4%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n360IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=1932ff3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FCORQTPOZCBKY5QHHYVOQ67GUJ4%2F&h=cfd305c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/CORQTPOZCBKY5QHHYVOQ67GUJ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n保安謂：「如果佢想起身唔使郁。」辯方質疑：「跌喺地唔郁點起身？」保安稱：「答你唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n保安證供與片不符 林朗彥脫襲擊罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港眾志去年3月到政總抗議送中惡法，其間與保安衝突。時任主席林朗彥（圖）當天衝入政總大堂後，遭指控撞跌保安兼壓其胸口，被控普通襲擊罪，案件昨花半日便審結。裁判官何俊堯裁決指，報稱遇襲的保安證供與現場片段有頗大出入，片段亦無法顯示事件細節，法庭不能肯定林有否接觸保安繼而動武，裁定林罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n保安梁炳森供稱，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PoSHnUxZ0UK3yPsH1DmCZmij3Us=/640x418/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z2MVJS3V4WTFHVISMFQ5V77Y2Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPoSHnUxZ0UK3yPsH1DmCZmij3Us%3D%2F640x418%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ2MVJS3V4WTFHVISMFQ5V77Y2Q.jpg&h=74bfd916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片段反證林遭壓倒<br />\n<br />\n保安在辯方盤問下承認，如他沒撲向前捉住林，他也不會跌倒；亦承認若他在林掙扎時放手，雙方便不會有身體接觸。至於林在地上掙扎時，會否只是想坐起或站起，<span class=\"orange\">保安謂：「如果佢想起身唔使郁。」辯方質疑：「跌喺地唔郁點起身？」保安稱：「答你唔到。」</span>其後辯方播片，指片段顯示實情是保安壓住林，而非林壓他，他攔截被告時也沒警告林別衝前。保安改口表示同意。<br />\n<br />\n何官裁決指，片段顯示不到林撞跌保安，卻見保安上前攔截林，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林朗彥在庭外表示，<span class=\"orange\">涉案片段反映保安作供不誠實，促糾正其「為入罪去扭曲事實」的態度。</span><br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2507/19"},{"pid":"d8feeafbb08be5e8b0442fa7130fec4f7c03e241","tid":2110563,"uid":39710,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"係咪又係啲前狗嚟"},{"pid":"37d922d7422bac199457e8d4f4a4d1ee213cce93","tid":2110563,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d8feeafbb08be5e8b0442fa7130fec4f7c03e241","tid":2110563,"uid":39710,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"係咪又係啲前狗嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"好多都係"},{"pid":"f3e11695acad0bddc6ccc6c04f86906bf1334502","tid":2110563,"uid":34553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d8feeafbb08be5e8b0442fa7130fec4f7c03e241","tid":2110563,"uid":39710,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"係咪又係啲前狗嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:15:54.000Z","msg":"立會保安基本上都係狗"},{"pid":"d97f41d6e16aac357177bec93ccf4fbe787d6be6","tid":2110563,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"所以點解有時被告周圍問人攞片<br />\n就係要反證人證供不實<br />\n唔好再戇鳩話舉證責任係控方"},{"pid":"572135b025c6ddf40f850e55f72ec8015e7f6e22","tid":2110563,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:24:03.000Z","msg":"做保安狗都有狗隊照？算老妨？"},{"pid":"6774ae8b2f0a0c30a43c5b516e7ba42a51de5fb6","tid":2110563,"uid":15592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37d922d7422bac199457e8d4f4a4d1ee213cce93","tid":2110563,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d8feeafbb08be5e8b0442fa7130fec4f7c03e241","tid":2110563,"uid":39710,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"係咪又係啲前狗嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"好多都係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"如果係現職就分分鐘俾官讚係誠實證人，再判埋林罪成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b879b16ee5803e1b87d4957879bd52fd268e18d","tid":2110563,"uid":176666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"而家法庭變左要被告自己舉證證明自己清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"c6321dcf9dfebe496acdf9de3878152ebf29efb3","tid":2110563,"uid":281916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:17:43.000Z","msg":"防礙司法公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8106dd5964ebb87a343522085fcb0490e3e00cda","tid":2110563,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:24:45.000Z","msg":"無論做邊份工都鐘意講大話"}]}